.TH HOSTS3D 1 "13 Apr 26"
.SH NAME
hosts3d \- 3D real-time network monitor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hosts3d \fR[\fB\-f\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B Hosts3D
is a 3D real-time network monitor that displays hosts and packet
traffic.  Features include support for multiple sensors, analysis of
packets to gather hostnames and services, configurable layout of
subnetworks, packet capture/replay, managed local \fBhsen\fR sensors,
and filtering by host, protocol tree, sensor, or port.
.TP
.B \-f
Display full screen.
.P
Press \fBH\fR in Hosts3D or open \fBHelp\fR from the right-click menu.
